## Decommission Criteria

Legacy system fully decommissioned when:
- [ ] All waves complete with 4+ weeks stability
- [ ] Zero production traffic routed to legacy
- [ ] Data migration verified (reconciliation report)
- [ ] Legacy monitoring removed from on-call runbooks
- [ ] Legal/compliance sign-off on legacy retirement
